text: Imay-Karmaly () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Imay-Karmalinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 330 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Imay-Karmaly
